name: Yahya goes to West Virginia
description: Yahya is the angel of death💀,his mission is to collect the souls of all people. Just before he was about to go back to heaven, he realized that he forgot a group of people, the "west virginians".  They are so full of life that they were the only ones remaining on earth, and you(Yahya the angel of death) have to go to West Virginia as fast as possible to take their souls.
